OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777471867
OL,3,CAI puts at least 'two million London
OL,4,Cjobs' at risk
OL,6,FAI is already transforming London but
OL,7,Fanalysis has found that more than two
OL,8,Fmillion people in London are in roles
OL,9,Fwhere GenAI could automate a share of
OL,10,Ftheir tasks, according to a new report
OL,11,Fby City Hall.
OL,13,FThis includes more than 300,000
OL,14,Fadministrative workers who face the
OL,15,Fhighest levels of exposure and risk of
OL,16,FAI automation, as their clerical tasks
OL,17,Falign most closely with GenAI
OL,18,Fcapabilities.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777471867
OL,3,CAI puts at least 'two million London
OL,4,Cjobs' at risk
OL,6,FIn addition, 748,000 workers could see
OL,7,FAI impact in tasks they do including
OL,8,Fjobs in IT, data and secretarial work.
OL,10,FWomen, who are disproportionately in
OL,11,Fadministrative and clerical roles,
OL,12,Fyoung people and those with higher
OL,13,Feducational levels are among the most
OL,14,Fexposed.
OL,16,FThe report found that jobs such as
OL,17,Fsales administrators, brokers, website
OL,18,Fdesigners, librarians and travel
OL,19,Fagents are most at risk.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777471867
OL,3,CAI puts at least 'two million London
OL,4,Cjobs' at risk
OL,6,FThe Mayor of London, Sir Sadiq Khan,
OL,7,Fwarned AI could cause "significant
OL,8,Fharm" if London isn't on top of AI's
OL,9,Fevolution on the job sector.
OL,11,FLondon faces high but uncertain impact
OL,12,Fwith at least 46% of London workers in
OL,13,Froles where AI could automate asks
OL,14,Fwhich is higher than the national
OL,15,Faverage of 38%, the report by
OL,16,Feconomist Jeff Dwan-O'Reilly said.
OL,18,FThe jobs least at risk include
OL,19,Farchitects, barbers, childminders,
OL,20,Fdriving instructors, undertakers, and
OL,21,Fchief executives.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777471867
OL,3,CAI puts at least 'two million London
OL,4,Cjobs' at risk
OL,6,FThe report warned that it did not
OL,7,Fimply "no impact" for the 54% of
OL,8,Fpeople who work in jobs less exposed
OL,9,Fto AI
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FSir Sadiq is expected to tell the
OL,17,FBloomberg CityLab Summit of mayors and
OL,18,Fpolicymakers in Madrid about the
OL,19,Fintroduction of the London AI and jobs
OL,20,Ftaskforce.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777471867
OL,3,CAI puts at least 'two million London
OL,4,Cjobs' at risk
OL,6,F"I want to be clear that a high degree
OL,7,Fof exposure to AI does not necessarily
OL,8,Fmean job losses.
OL,10,F"Our research indicates there's every
OL,11,Fchance that AI will augment and assist
OL,12,Fthe Londoners working in these roles,
OL,13,Frather than eliminating their jobs
OL,14,Fcompletely.
OL,16,F"But given the numbers of Londoners
OL,17,Fthat are exposed ` and the finding
OL,18,Fthat 7% of large UK businesses have
OL,19,Falready used AI to cut staff ` we
OL,20,Fcannot afford to be complacent."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
