PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1777471867
OL,3,CAI puts at least 'two million London
OL,4,Cjobs' at risk
OL,6,FThe introduction of London AI and jobs
OL,7,Ftaskforce will continue analysis of
OL,8,Fthe job sector in the capital and
OL,9,Fbetter understand the AI impact on
OL,10,Fjobs, productivity, inclusion, and job
OL,11,Fquality, and guide policy responses.
OL,13,FThe taskforce will bring together
OL,14,Fexpertise from within government, the
OL,15,Fbusiness community, trade unions the
OL,16,Fskills sector and the AI industry.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
